CORRECTIVE ACTION:
The following actions have been made for correction:
1. Before outings staff will get with children and lay out expectations with youth.  Which is in line with TBRI training.  Listen and mind and stick together
2. Sunny Glen will ensure that adequate staff is available for outings to meet child caregiver ratio or above.  Youth will be assigned to specific staff.  That staff will be responsible for the youth assigned to them.
